Accessory boat that can be towed with the Utility Unit. Requires Swift Water Rescue trained personnel to operate.
The boat trailer cannot be assigned personnel,
either assign your trained personnel to the towing vehicle, or assign them to a separate unit en route.

either assign your trained personnel to the towing vehicle, or assign them to a separate unit en route.
